{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ca0f43156c","title":"李富春接见国家计委同志谈斗争薄一波","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33b3995d11","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":6,"articleId":"ca0f43156c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"李富春","id":"25e2abfb25","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘澜涛","id":"3dcf7883ce","type":"人物"},{"name":"重要党内斗争和案件","id":"83b1479e48","type":"主题"},{"name":"张闻天","id":"b0e4f99ee9","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"薄一波","id":"d54ab0cc80","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"9c4175f9ee","name":"李富春"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3aa5c85f7d","type":"title","text":"李富春接见国家计委同志谈斗争薄一波","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca0f43156c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"19608c8a53","type":"paragraph","text":"摘要：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca0f43156c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0886ba30a2","type":"paragraph","text":"斗争薄一波，要挖他的历史根子，要挖痛。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca0f43156c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c076a9717","type":"paragraph","text":"第一、挖（他）是刘少奇包庇下来的叛徒（下边未听清）。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca0f43156c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5875e853c2","type":"paragraph","text":"第二、投奔阎锡山，把大叛徒宋劭文、牛佩琮、戎子和等搞到山西去。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca0f43156c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f2a2762b5","type":"paragraph","text":"第三、抗战时期搞“牺盟会”、“决死队”。“牺盟会”负责人是戎子和（下一个未听清）。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca0f43156c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8aa4f3cee","type":"paragraph","text":"第四、薄一波的一套手法是阎锡山那里来的，以后和刘少奇、刘澜涛、安子文等大叛徒勾结起来，到处伸手。你搞他的具体问题，他可以躲闪。你搞他的历史问题，他就没有办法。自首叛变61个人，是刘少奇批的，没有报告主席，没有报告中央，是同张闻天勾结起来搞的，主席不知道。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ca0f43156c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}